  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2003-09-23",
    "date": "2003-11-03T21:36:39Z",
    "text": "Combat Pay Safeguard Act of 2003 - Requires the total monthly rate for all combat zone-related special pay and allowances (hardship duty pay, special pay for duty subject to hostile fire or imminent danger, and the family separation allowance) available after September 30, 2003, for members of the armed forces serving in a combat zone designated for Operations Iraqi Freedom or Enduring Freedom to be at least equal to the rate in effect for September 2003."
  },
